    {
      "id": "scene_01",
      "speaker": "我",
      "text": "当我推开实验室沉重的大门时，灰尘在阳光下飞舞。那是她第一次回头看我。",
      "bg": "bg_lab",
      "sprites": {
        "left": null,
        "center": "girl_sad",
        "right": null,
        "active": "center"
      },
      "bgm": null,
      "se": null,
      "next": "choice_01",
      "effect": "none"
    },
    {
      "id": "choice_01",
      "speaker": "少女",
      "text": "“你...也是来终结这一切的吗？”她的眼神里透着绝望。",
      "bg": "bg_lab",
      "sprites": {
        "left": null,
        "center": "girl_sad",
        "right": null,
        "active": "center"
      },
      "bgm": null,
      "se": null,
      "options": [
        { "text": "安慰她", "next": "path_happy" },
        { "text": "沉默地走近", "next": "path_sad" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "path_happy",
      "speaker": "我",
      "text": "“不，我是来带你离开这里的。”",
      "bg": "bg_lab",
      "sprites": {
        "left": null,
        "center": "girl_happy",
        "right": null,
        "active": "center"
